OL,7,FElectronic ankle tags are being fitted
OL,8,Fto prolific shoplifters in Sussex to
OL,9,Ftry to stop reoffending.
OL,11,FSussex Police said it was the first
OL,12,Fforce in the country to use GPS
OL,13,Fdevices to tag shoplifters.
OL,15,FThe pilot project called Operation
OL,16,FSTOP will see repeat shoplifting
OL,17,Foffenders issued with Buddi tags.
