OL,7,FPolice said the tags will allow
OL,8,Fofficers to monitor the movements of
OL,9,Foffenders in real time and enable
OL,10,F"swift action if breaches or tampering
OL,11,Foccur".
OL,13,FVictoria Hale, 50, of Command Road in
OL,14,FEastbourne, became the first person to
OL,15,Fbe fitted with a Buddi tag at Brighton
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court in September.
OL,18,FShe had been given a two-year Criminal
OL,19,FBehaviour Order (CBO) after pleading
OL,20,Fguilty to 12 shoplifting charges.
