OL,7,FDuring a separate investigation, Barry
OL,8,FFarthing, 41, of Hughenden Road,
OL,9,FHastings, was jailed for eight months
OL,10,Ffollowing a six-week shoplifting spree
OL,11,Fin East Sussex.
OL,13,FHe was also given a CBO and a location
OL,14,Fmonitoring tag to wear for 12 months
OL,15,Fwhen he is released from prison.
OL,17,FChief Superintendent Katy Woolford
OL,18,Fsaid: "Shoplifting has an enormous
OL,19,Fimpact on businesses and the wider
OL,20,Fcommunity.
